  "description": "TEP-H0 tests an environment-dependent Cepheid timing bias in the SH0ES sample, finding H0-sigma correlations with a robust combined environmental slope Gamma_X~2.3x10^7. In the TEP-native pure-Cepheid gauge (beta_X=0) this corresponds to kappa_equiv~7.3x10^5 mag, yielding unified H0^TEP=68.84 km/s/Mpc.",
